3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/e4e3ed45-f463-4420-b066-c1a71c728b29/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/924af7f8-273d-4e12-8ddc-217db2187c8b.png" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" width="1536" height="1024" natural-width="1536" natural-height="1024" data-lg-size="3000x3000"></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1741444927819" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1741444927819"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>In der heutigen schnelllebigen Welt zählen Bequemlichkeit und Effizienz mehr denn je. Genau das bietet der IronJet – ein innovativer Hand-Dampfer, der Ihre Kleiderpflege revolutioniert. Mit einer ultraschnellen Aufheizzeit von nur 15 Sekunden, einem eleganten Design und kraftvoller Dampfleistung verwandelt er das Entfernen von Falten in eine schnelle, mühelose Aufgabe. Ob im Alltag, auf Reisen oder für besondere Anlässe – der IronJet ist Ihr idealer Begleiter für gepflegte Kleidung im Handumdrehen.</p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1715753003432" class="gf_row gf_equal-height" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1715753003432" data-layout-lg="6+6" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="6+6" data-layout-sm="6+6" data-layout-xs="12+12" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; visibility: visible;"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1715753003430" data-id="1715753003430" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1715753020114" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1715753020114" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://9bqdz6102nuri75t-81568891219.shopifypreview.com/cdn/shop/files/2025_GARTEN_GERMAN_1_1296x.png?v=1751883538" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" width="1080" height="1080" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1080" natural-height="1080" data-lg-size="3000x3000"></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1715753005227" data-id="1715753005227" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1715753025516" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1715753025516"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h1 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><font color="#000000"><b>1. Aufgeheizt in 15 Sekunden</b></font></h1></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1715753059830" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1715753059830"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><font color="#000000"><strong>Nie wieder Warten</strong></font></p><p><font color="#000000">Dank moderner Schnellaufheiz-Technologie ist der Steamer in nur 15 Sekunden einsatzbereit. Ob Sie es eilig zur Arbeit haben oder sich auf einen wichtigen Termin vorbereiten – Sie erhalten sofort leistungsstarken Dampf, ohne Verzögerung. Kein langes Vorheizen wie bei herkömmlichen Bügeleisen – einfach einstecken und losdampfen.</font></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1715753190022" class="gf_row gf_equal-height" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1715753190022" data-layout-lg="6+6" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="6+6" data-layout-sm="6+6" data-layout-xs="12+12" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; visibility: visible;"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1715753003430" data-id="1715753003430" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1715753190023" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1715753190023" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0815/6889/1219/files/7_c6a7db2e-b3f3-48cb-8d2c-e58550b64bdd_120x120.jpg?v=1751641087" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" width="1080" height="1080" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1080" natural-height="1080" data-lg-size="3000x3000"></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1715753005227" data-id="1715753005227" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; min-height: auto;"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1715753190046" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1715753190046"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h1 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><font color="#000000"><b>2. Einhändige Bedienung</b></font></h1></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1715753190025" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="17